State.Name: Wasteland Venturers Sim Settlements 2 Addon Pack
State.Author: Tinuvia and Myrmarachne
State.Description: Adds 150 building plans to Sim Settlements 2. Scrappy, lived-in, detailed homes, farms, shops, scrap yards, toilets and bookstores. Kick off your muddy boots, take a swig of rum from a dirty cup. Bloat yourself on Pizza and Raider Burgers. Top it off with Wasteland Ice Cream, Coffee and Cinnamon Buns. Welcome back, welcome home!

State.Name: WAVE - Wave Animation Vanilla Enhanced
State.Author: SparrowPrince
State.Description: No more elastic waves in the Commonwealth. Brand new effects and textures with a more realistic motion.

State.Name: We Are The Minutemen
State.Author: TheFirstEnD
State.Description: The Minutemen are supposed to be the best alternative for rebuilding the Commonwealth because : More settlements = More resources = Better materials = Better fire power and a larger presence in all the Commonwealth. But currently this is not the case and this mod attempts to fix this problem.

State.Name: We Are The Minutemen - Militarized Minutemen - Uniform Patches and Insignia Addon - Compatibility Patch
State.Author: creodron
State.Description: A custom compatibility patch between We Are The Minutemen, Militarized Minutemen, and Militarized Minutemen Uniform Patches and Insignia Addon.

State.Name: Weapon Wall Racks (WWR)
State.Author: jkruse05
State.Description: Modular storage racks to attach to walls.

State.Name: Weston Water LOD Fix
State.Author: ossumpossum
State.Description: Flags water at the Weston Water Treatment Plant with IsFullLOD so it is visible and no longer pops in.

State.Name: WET - Water Enhancement Textures
State.Author: SparrowPrince
State.Description: WET enhances all water and most water-related effects in the game. From one of the creators of the popular Realistic Water Two mod for Skyrim.

State.Name: Wetness Shader Fix
State.Author: Ablaze666
State.Description: This small mod fixes the exaggerated shine of specific objects while it's raining.

State.Name: Wetness Shader Fix
State.Author: Ablaze666
State.Description: This small mod fixes the exaggerated shine of specific objects while it's raining.

State.Name: Whisper's Extra Pieces and Snaps
State.Author: Whisper and Karvoc and Others
State.Description: Some extra kitbashed floors and ceilings, and extra snap-points upon many vanilla wood/metal build-items.

State.Name: Whisper's Institute Build Kit
State.Author: Whisper
State.Description: For those who think the Institute is missing out on sampling and experimenting on the surface. Here are several snapping Institute build pieces, workbenches, furniture, generators, connectors, decor - the whole shebang of what I could figure a group of Institute researchers would want.

State.Name: Whisper's Institute Build Kit

State.Name: Wireless Workshop Items

State.Description: Hate wires? Here are a few of the basic and DLC workshop items converted to use wireless power.

State.Name: Workshop Framework
State.Author: kinggath
State.Description:
Framework to open up the settlement system to editing by the community.



For Players: New controls and faster, more stable workshop scripts.



For Modders: Add new resource types, override settings, and generally change the way settlements work dynamically.

State.Name: Workshop Plus
State.Author: kinggath
State.Description:
Transforms Workshop mode into a God simulator - giving you all of the tools you need to create amazing settlements. 



Flight, Undo Buttons, Layers, Cloning Tools, Free Build Mode, and more!

State.Name: Bullet Counted Reload System (BCR)
State.Author: shavkacagarikia
State.Description: Finally, a proper engine-level system for bullet counted reloads with most of the features such a system should have.

State.Name: Better Console - F4SE
State.Author: Kassent
State.Description: This is a F4SE plugin which makes console menu show extra useful infomation about selected target,for example, target's name, ID, baseID, mod name and so on.This plugin also add some extra info lists to console to show selected actor's all kinds of info like factions, perks, active effects, actor values, equipments and so on.

State.Name: Bullet Counted Reload System (BCR)

State.Description: Finally, a proper engine-level system for bullet counted reloads with most of the features such a system should have.

State.Description: This mod adds a clock widget to loading menu, main menu and fader menu to display current real time while loading.How much time did you spend on loading?

State.Name: DEF_UI Iconlibs Rescaled and Fixed
State.Author: Phlunder
State.Description: Aims to bring consistency in design and coloring to the icon library. Also fixes various issues with icon sizes, bounding boxes, and scaling.

State.Name: EBF UFO4P compatibility fix
State.Author: Peregrin0
State.Description: Compatibility patch for Everyone's Best Friend (EBF) and version 2.1.0 of the Unofficial Fallout 4 Patch (UFO4P). Both modify the same Papyrus script files causing one to override the corrections of the other. This mod merges the script changes.

State.Name: FallUI - Inventory
State.Author: m8r98a4f2
State.Description: This is FallUI - Inventory. A optimized Fallout 4 inventory interface for PC.

State.Name: FallUI - Confirm Boxes (incl. Yes Im Sure)
State.Author: m8r98a4f2
State.Description: Overhaul of all confirm box interfaces. Including different designs and styles for many box types (configurable). You can also choose to disable confirms, so it automatically accept without confirmation (like "Yes Im Sure"). Interface covers all languages.

State.Name: FallUI - HUD
State.Author: m8r98a4f2
State.Description: A highly configurable HUD. Every widget can be positioned and configured. Configure your design in the in-game layout manager in MCM. Layouts can be shared and imported too.

Archives.Name: Full Dialogue Interface - All languages - NMM installer - Beta12-1235-Beta12.zip

State.Name: Full Dialogue Interface (NewDialog English and CN-DE-ES-FR-IT-JA-PL-PTBR-RU translations)
State.Author: Cirosan and shadwar
State.Description: Makes the game display the full lines of what your character is going to say in conversation, instead of just a paraphrase. It also revamps the interface so that the game will now display dialogue options in a list and use the number keys/face buttons for input, depending on your control scheme. Supports both keyboard and gamepad.

State.Name: Mod Configuration Menu
State.Author: reg2k - Neanka - shadowslasher410
State.Description: The Mod Configuration Menu is a settings page for mods! It provides a central location for mod configuration, accessible via the Pause menu.

State.Name: Faster Workshop (Workshop Lag Fix)
State.Author: reg2k
State.Description: Faster Workshop is an F4SE plugin that optimizes workshop loading times by replacing some of the most expensive and inefficient regions of workshop loading code with far more efficient versions. Also provides a hotkey to instantly enter Workshop mode and fixes workshop icon load lag.

Untie the game speed from the framerate. Fixes physical bugs. Reduces loading time.

Now there is a separate version for VR.
